query:
SELECT sp.id, sp.accountId, sp.projectId, sp.content, sp.postUrl, a.deviceId, a.username 
FROM scheduled_posts sp 
JOIN accounts a ON sp.accountId = a.id 
WHERE sp.status = 'posted' AND sp.postUrl IS NOT NULL 
LIMIT 20
